Comment: 10,0:00:00.98,0:01:30.86,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,OP
Dialogue: 10,0:01:35.17,0:01:36.24,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,I didn't expect that.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:36.83,0:01:37.85,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:38.61,0:01:39.49,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:42.12,0:01:45.87,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Kakeru-kun, do you really like me?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:49.96,0:01:50.98,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:51.58,0:01:52.59,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:53.43,0:01:56.52,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Am I only fooling myself that I do?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:57.26,0:01:58.05,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:59.07,0:02:02.68,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Am I just trying to validate myself?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:03.20,0:02:07.05,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,The snow's still falling all around me.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:07.05,0:02:09.47,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,But you're not seeing it, Kakeru-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:10.26,0:02:12.77,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,I don't think we understand anything about each other.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:13.94,0:02:14.81,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:15.47,0:02:17.11,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,I don't see any snow.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:25.30,0:02:28.76,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,I was thinking of asking my mother\Nto play the piano for me some time.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:28.76,0:02:30.62,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,I'd like you to hear it as well.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:30.62,0:02:32.50,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Your mother's piano?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:32.50,0:02:33.53,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,That sounds wonderful.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:34.83,0:02:38.35,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,She's a professional pianist, so I know she'll treat it like a real performance.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.35,0:02:39.28,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:40.64,0:02:42.10,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,And, what?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:43.43,0:02:44.06,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,You should come.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:44.88,0:02:48.76,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Do you think we'll understand\Nmore about us if I do?{us as in the weird abilities they have}{yea i think that's implied so it should be ok}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:49.64,0:02:51.27,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,I'll give her a call now.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.87,0:02:53.02,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Hopefully she's free tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:54.68,0:02:56.40,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,Hello, Okikura residence.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:56.40,0:02:57.28,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Mom.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.28,0:02:58.26,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,Kakeru?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.26,0:02:59.49,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:59.49,0:03:01.58,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,There's someone I've been hanging out with recently,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.58,0:03:04.16,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,and I was hoping you could play the piano for them.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:04.55,0:03:06.50,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,Oh, that's unusual, coming from you.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:06.50,0:03:08.88,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,I don't think you've ever asked that before.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.88,0:03:09.58,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:10.05,0:03:11.28,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,I'd love to.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.28,0:03:13.98,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,I might as well play a few pieces.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:13.98,0:03:16.71,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,Oh, why don't you invite their parents too?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.71,0:03:18.03,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Good idea.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.03,0:03:19.42,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Thanks, Mom.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.10,0:03:20.92,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,Kakeru...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.92,0:03:21.40,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.19,0:03:24.53,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,What's the verdict on our\Nearlier conversation?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.25,0:03:26.12,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Verdict?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.72,0:03:28.22,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,How about coming with me?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.08,0:03:31.12,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,I'm still thinking about it.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:31.88,0:03:36.11,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,So I'm guessing you're using \NFukami-san's cellphone right now?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:37.22,0:03:39.05,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,I already had the chance to meet her.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.05,0:03:42.23,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,She happened to drop by once when you weren't here.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.23,0:03:43.12,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.74,0:03:44.71,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.74,0:03:47.62,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,She's a kind girl who has trouble being decisive,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.46,0:03:51.61,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,and she pushes herself to keep the people around her happy.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.49,0:03:55.30,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,I've only made things more difficult for her.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.30,0:03:58.30,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,But she was the one who showed me how little I really know.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.26,0:04:00.23,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:00.23,0:04:01.17,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,You really like her.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.35,0:04:03.18,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.96,0:04:08.64,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Let's head home.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.97,0:04:13.56,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,I think I'll stay here a bit longer.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.90,0:04:14.73,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.15,0:04:19.48,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,I feel like this is where my summer began.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.10,0:04:21.56,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,So I'd like to stay here.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.56,0:04:23.59,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,This is where I belong.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.59,0:04:24.72,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:25.48,0:04:26.59,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,"Belong?"
Dialogue: 10,0:04:26.59,0:04:28.58,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,It's something Sacchan told me.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.12,0:04:32.90,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Depending on the time, the occasion, and the people with you,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.90,0:04:36.08,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,an ordinary place can become somewhere very special.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.01,0:04:40.66,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Don't stay out too late.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.66,0:04:41.32,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.03,0:04:44.72,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Then I'll see you at my place tomorrow afternoon.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.82,0:04:46.51,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.99,0:05:03.07,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Hey, Hina-chan?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.52,0:05:05.02,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Could you do me a favor?{"Do me a favor." if too long}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.02,0:05:07.54,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'll be back by tomorrow morning,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.54,0:05:10.49,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,so could you make sure Mom and Dad don't worry about me? Please?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.49,0:05:11.68,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.68,0:05:13.26,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Bye, then. I'm hanging up.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.95,0:05:18.88,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,Onee-chan, no way!{lol}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.13,0:05:37.41,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.41,0:05:38.35,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.35,0:05:39.90,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,You're home late today.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.79,0:05:42.37,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.14,0:05:46.49,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,Oh, welcome back, Onee-chan.{top lel}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.28,0:05:52.82,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,I hope she's all right.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:52.82,0:05:54.46,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,Girls, dinner's ready!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.46,0:05:55.50,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,C-Coming!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.29,0:06:00.59,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,Onee-chan said she'll eat later.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.48,0:06:13.01,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,Thanks for the food!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.01,0:06:15.89,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,Oh, she said that she's not that hungry, so she'll just have a little.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.38,0:06:18.62,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,What a picky sister she is.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.62,0:06:19.27,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.65,0:06:25.74,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,I want to go hiking again.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.09,0:06:26.91,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.91,0:06:27.85,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.85,0:06:29.05,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.05,0:06:30.96,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,Hiking is great, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.96,0:06:33.02,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,I wonder if Sis can take us up this week.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.02,0:06:35.33,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,No, I want to climb from the bottom.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.90,0:06:36.40,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.98,0:06:43.14,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,How's...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.01,0:06:45.74,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,your knee?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.21,0:06:51.64,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,The trainer who looked after me\Nat the camp said it should be all good.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.30,0:06:52.81,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.76,0:06:55.32,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,I'm glad I went to that camp.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:56.01,0:06:58.56,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Are you going to go back to your\Nclub once the second term starts?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.12,0:07:01.85,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,Coach reckons I should.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.29,0:07:03.45,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,I guess I will.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.06,0:07:05.78,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,Though...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.37,0:07:10.03,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,I bet I know nothing about what you do, Yanagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.19,0:07:12.82,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,You wanna come watch me during my lessons?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:13.64,0:07:14.40,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.67,0:07:40.31,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,You're still here?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.73,0:07:42.72,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Look who's talking!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.72,0:07:45.06,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,You said you'd go home soon.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.56,0:08:20.13,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,I wonder if I'll belong here too if I stay the night.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:21.28,0:08:22.68,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Oh, that's...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.68,0:08:24.73,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,If I were to find a place where I belonged...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.57,0:08:28.98,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Would you no longer experience that \N"sudden but foreseeable loneliness" of yours?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.61,0:08:34.17,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Is it still snowing?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.80,0:08:37.26,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,No, not anymore.
Comment: 10,0:09:14.90,0:09:21.12,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,eyecatch
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.95,0:09:27.77,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,Good morning, Kakeru.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.87,0:09:30.29,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,About your call yesterday—
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.82,0:09:33.31,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,He stayed out again?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.01,0:09:38.68,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:40.86,0:09:43.04,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,Will Fukami-san's parents be coming?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.68,0:09:44.39,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.80,0:09:48.93,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,In that case, let's ask them to come a bit earlier and join us for a meal.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.93,0:09:49.90,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.57,0:09:57.92,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,You {\i1}are{\i0} going to tell Touko, aren't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.59,0:09:59.52,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.52,0:10:01.46,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,You're still being indecisive?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:01.46,0:10:04.82,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Just because you have Touko doesn't mean you'll be able to escape from your fate.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.82,0:10:06.91,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Yes, I know.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.11,0:10:38.82,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Wh-What?{hina's face}{this should be release pic}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.82,0:10:42.13,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,I was just thinking that you can really \Ntake charge when it comes down to it.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.13,0:10:43.68,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.68,0:10:48.75,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,Those are the highest words of praise used at \NHinode Beach Middle School's Girls' Swim Club.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:48.75,0:10:50.40,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.34,0:10:54.92,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,I'm not carrying anything?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:55.32,0:10:56.99,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,I'm not doing this because I'm a nice guy.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.99,0:10:59.14,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,This is for your safety, Sacchan.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.14,0:11:01.54,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,You don't seem to have a lot of confidence in me.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:01.54,0:11:04.89,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,I'm a bit concerned for your health, so I'd rather play it safe.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.97,0:11:06.52,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.92,0:11:08.98,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,I'm here for you!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.16,0:11:11.98,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.33,0:11:34.85,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.67,0:11:36.71,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.10,0:11:37.78,Glasslip-Main,Dad,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.78,0:11:38.90,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:38.90,0:11:41.01,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,I won't be needing any breakfast.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.01,0:11:43.26,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,Oh? That's a surprise, Hina.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.87,0:11:46.85,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,A few things happened last night, and I ate way too much.{I went through some shit}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:46.85,0:11:48.14,Glasslip-Main,Dad,0,0,0,,"A few things?"
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.14,0:11:50.18,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,I feel like I could eat a horse!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.97,0:11:52.03,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,I'm so hungry!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.03,0:11:53.84,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Wow, it looks delicious!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.84,0:11:57.65,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Oh, Mom, if Hina-chan's not eating, I'll have hers too!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.79,0:12:14.66,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,Grab on to those tree roots.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.66,0:12:15.42,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.37,0:12:40.86,Glasslip-Main,Dad,0,0,0,,That sounds great. I'd love to go.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.86,0:12:42.68,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,What about you, Mom?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.68,0:12:43.60,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,Count me in too!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.60,0:12:44.87,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,All right, then!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.87,0:12:47.06,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,Time to bust out that dress!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.31,0:12:51.30,Glasslip-Main,Dad,0,0,0,,Guess I'll blow through the rest of today's work.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.30,0:12:52.75,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,I'll help you!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:02.93,0:14:04.03,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.03,0:14:05.95,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Everyone was like, "Who is he?"
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.95,0:14:07.17,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,"Is he someone special?"
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.17,0:14:08.03,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,You made such a stir!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.66,0:14:10.74,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.85,0:14:13.85,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,So, what did you think?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:14.86,0:14:15.72,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,Think?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.72,0:14:17.21,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Yeah. What did you think?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.32,0:14:22.71,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,You were the best dancer, as well as the prettiest.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.00,0:14:31.71,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,You're going to move out\Nafter you graduate, aren't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.61,0:14:39.44,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.96,0:14:43.25,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,I did my part yesterday!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:46.00,0:14:50.16,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,Um, will you be going to Hinode Beach High School with Onee-chan {from}starting next semester?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.44,0:14:56.05,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,I haven't sorted out my transfer procedures just yet.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:56.05,0:14:57.29,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,What're you guys talking about?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.29,0:15:00.08,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,O-Oh, sorry. I'll give you guys some space.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.87,0:15:02.71,Glasslip-Main,Dad,0,0,0,,Hina-san, would you like some cake?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.40,0:15:05.40,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,I'd love some!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:05.40,0:15:07.17,Glasslip-Main,Dad,0,0,0,,Kakeru, why don't you come for some—
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.17,0:15:09.92,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Sorry, we were just about to go for a stroll.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.99,0:15:12.93,Glasslip-Main,Mom,0,0,0,,We'll get started at five-thirty.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.93,0:15:13.64,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.73,0:15:19.69,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,So you really wanna run with me?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.26,0:15:22.29,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,I never said that.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.29,0:15:24.19,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,But it's kind of a habit now, so I might as well.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.53,0:15:42.33,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,Help yourself.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.38,0:15:46.13,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,This is great!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.97,0:15:53.82,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,There are pickled leeks, stuffed tomatoes, \Nsoy-boiled spinach, fried tofu, and egg rolls.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.31,0:15:56.89,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,Sorry. I'll get you some chopsticks.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.61,0:15:58.30,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.30,0:15:59.33,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.90,0:16:04.68,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,The other day,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.31,0:16:07.53,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,at the Kirinkan...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.53,0:16:09.54,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,Yeah? What about it?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.84,0:16:12.55,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,There's something I didn't tell you.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.01,0:16:16.74,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.26,0:16:25.95,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,I was so cruel, getting you involved like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.06,0:16:27.79,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.66,0:16:36.45,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,So this hiking trip was...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.27,0:16:38.93,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,"For tomorrow."
Dialogue: 10,0:16:41.62,0:16:42.88,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.17,0:16:54.70,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,My father's a glass artisan, so I've been looking at sparkly objects since I was a kid.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.54,0:16:58.70,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,I'm not sure what these visions are anymore,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.14,0:17:02.00,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,but I wonder when I first started seeing them.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.76,0:17:06.27,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Lend me yours for a sec.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.88,0:17:07.71,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:14.18,0:17:16.97,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,We'll be able to test this soon.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.97,0:17:18.96,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,It'd be nice if we found something out.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.96,0:17:20.17,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.17,0:17:23.32,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,But I also wouldn't mind if we found nothing.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.32,0:17:23.85,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.84,0:17:32.16,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,I never would've thought both our families would come together to listen to my mother's piano.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.16,0:17:34.79,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Isn't that something to be happy about on its own?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:34.79,0:17:37.25,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Kakeru-kun, are you...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.25,0:17:37.91,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.88,0:17:40.45,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,I'm a little scared of knowing.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.16,0:18:10.98,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Can you see it too, Kakeru-kun?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.98,0:18:11.70,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.47,0:18:38.85,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,Going downhill is pretty tough on your knees, isn't it?{it's an eccentric activity!}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.80,0:18:49.27,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,Can you hear my voice?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.77,0:18:51.70,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,Yeah, I can hear you.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:53.17,0:18:57.78,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,It feels a bit strange not being able\Nto see someone who's close, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.80,0:19:00.97,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,Can you see me from where you are, Sacchan?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.14,0:19:04.43,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,No, not yet.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.03,0:19:15.75,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.83,0:19:20.49,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,I think I'm afraid of being together with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.49,0:19:21.01,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.43,0:19:26.77,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Mom has asked me to accompany her around the world on her concert tour.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.38,0:19:29.71,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Kakeru-kun, what are you saying?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:29.71,0:19:33.06,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,Do you mean that soon,\Nyou might not be here anymore?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:34.17,0:19:39.82,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,I don't think I can take experiencing that sudden but foreseeable loneliness every winter anymore.{I'm assuming this should be consistent, so I'm changing it to match the other instances.}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.90,0:19:46.03,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,But we spent all of yesterday together!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.51,0:19:51.54,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,We're back.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.12,0:19:54.05,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,Onee-chan, hurry up!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.05,0:19:55.89,Glasslip-Main,Hina,0,0,0,,She's about to start!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.41,0:20:02.16,Glasslip-Main,Dad,0,0,0,,Take a seat, you two.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:06.45,0:20:09.02,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,If the fragments really are glimpses of the future,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.24,0:20:13.47,Glasslip-Main,Touko,0,0,0,,that means that we'll be together\Nfor the fireworks next year, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.91,0:20:44.82,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,Once we're down at the bottom,\Nlet's go to Kazemichi.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:44.82,0:20:45.72,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,My pleasure!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.12,0:20:57.18,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Why're you stopping?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.24,0:21:01.61,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,I need to talk to Touko again.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.57,0:21:08.52,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,It's been a while since we've been to Kazemichi. Wanna go?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:08.52,0:21:09.62,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,I guess.
Comment: 10,0:21:59.88,0:23:29.84,Glasslip-Main,,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 10,0:23:30.78,0:23:32.97,Glasslip-Main,Kakeru,0,0,0,,Guys, introduce yourselves too.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:32.97,0:23:33.97,Glasslip-Main,Hiro,0,0,0,,I'm Shirosaki Hiro.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:33.97,0:23:34.97,Glasslip-Main,Yanagi,0,0,0,,Takayama Yanagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:34.97,0:23:36.07,Glasslip-Main,Yuki,0,0,0,,I'm Imi Yukinari.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:36.07,0:23:38.06,Glasslip-Main,Sachi,0,0,0,,I'm Nagamiya Sachi.
