Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.31,0:22:14.02,ED-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}and bring me back to life again.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:21.91,0:22:26.38,ED-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}Hearts are fragile like glass
Dialogue: 1,0:22:27.08,0:22:31.26,ED-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}and shatter into pieces when they're broken.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:32.30,0:22:37.72,ED-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}I gingerly wrapped those of mine and sent them to you.
